.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45ed858190ab6349492107711bd97c9cfbceccc","tid":2352680,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"高過菲律賓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd197823fa33b86bdfde844207e89d45fe9cf481","tid":2352680,"uid":45376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:45:23.000Z","msg":"歐美堆左膠最鍾意自我批判歐美嘅資本主義點剝削平民<br />\n讚賞支那社會夠晒先進公平<br />\n希望佢地可以分享幾句"},{"pid":"c1e30a6f8980fbd3b4c6f41dd08a7c4b1e8e6076","tid":2352680,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"040b3aebd3a2770af1d0f1eb36b4051a8d3ac71a","tid":2352680,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"只需要將貧窮線下降就得啦, 拉"},{"pid":"f4562dca1af4b54778842c07a79b3cb957b22403","tid":2352680,"uid":360467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7f6f73f350d64914c62ec78e10d7eed6d3c0d6","tid":2352680,"uid":224560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"又話2020滅窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"武肺死鳩哂啲人咪滅貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5a9d4077fc5b3b49d5866864101727b3e03721","tid":2352680,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T23:36:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5ee5bab9f3b2cee828ba1b727d6df7839a9300be","tid":2352680,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T23:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a80455b719409f3ff9d7491a0623f